# 4-team football knockout, scripted end-to-end
new-tournament WorldCup football
add-stage knockout Final
register Eagles
register Tigers
register Sharks
register Wolves
close-registration
publish
start-tournament
# Semi 1
start-match next
action goal home 10
finish-period
finish-period
# Semi 2
start-match next
action goal home 10
finish-period
finish-period
# Final
start-match next
action goal home 10
finish-period
finish-period
advance-stage
show winner
quit
